data.description: Welcome to 915 Wayland Ct. a hidden gem, with charming neighborhood vibes and easy access to Smyrna Market Village, Truist Park and the Battery. This must see ,brick ranch style home sits on a corner lot with massive curb appeal and a delightful backyard perfect for entertaining family and friends. Inside, the blend of modern chic and timeless charm creates a warm and welcoming atmosphere. Hardwood floors are dominant throughout the home and just beyond the swanky dining area is a beautifully updated kitchen with quartz countertops, backsplash, and new stainless steel appliances. With three bedrooms and two baths, there's plenty of space for comfort and relaxation.This home is picture perfect in a well established community, with the added bonus of NO HOA. The seller's have loved this home to the max, and hope that you will do the same..
